A Slasher Demon is an elite version of the Ripper Demon. Slasher demons are guaranteed to spawn during Slayer assignments; otherwise, they have a spawn rate of 1 in 1,000. Elite spawn rates can be further increased with the use of fellstalk incense sticks and tier 3 luck.
